Note:
==============================================================================
Currency - Typed currency identity registry
==============================================================================

A Currency value is a small Integer (a "currency_id") that identifies a fiat,
crypto, or sovereign currency. The integer is INTERNAL and does NOT match the
ISO 4217 numeric code (the numeric code is one of several attributes carried
in the registry record). Identity is by registry slot; attributes are by
lookup.

The registry is a flat, compile-time-shaped table of records. Each record
carries:
    iso_alpha       - 3-letter ISO 4217 alpha code (or 3-4 char crypto/native)
    iso_numeric     - ISO 4217 numeric code (-1 for non-ISO entries)
    display_name    - English display name (UTF-8 string)
    symbol          - Currency symbol (UTF-8 string: "$", "EUR", "BTC", "SC")
    decimal_exponent - Minor-unit decimal exponent (USD=2, JPY=0, BTC=8,
                       SC=18 for smart-contract wei-style precision)
    classification  - CURRENCY_CLASS_* family flag
                       (FIAT, CRYPTO, SOVEREIGN, COMMODITY)

Public surface is FUNCTIONAL: callers use currency_from_iso_code("USD"),
currency_from_numeric_code(840), and accessor procs. No raw integer is
exposed in user-facing APIs except as an opaque handle.

Per ISO 4217:2015, alpha codes are immutable identifiers; numeric codes are
also stable; minor-unit "exponent" defines the number of decimal places in
the minor representation (so amount * 10^-exponent yields the major unit).

This file provides registry slots for:
  - Active ISO 4217 fiat currencies in worldwide circulation
  - Major cryptocurrencies (BTC, ETH, stablecoins, top L1/L2 tokens)
  - SC (sovereign-scale digital credit primitive, wei-style precision)

References:
  - ISO 4217:2015 "Codes for the representation of currencies"
  - SIX Financial Information ISO 4217 maintenance list
  - BIP 32 / EIP-20 token registry conventions
:End Note

Import "compiler/frontend/primitives/memory/layout.runa" as Layout
Import "compiler/frontend/primitives/core/memory_core.runa" as MemoryCore
Import "compiler/frontend/primitives/core/string_core.runa" as StringCore

